item.title: CVE-2022-33146|2024-08-03T08:01:20.099Z -- web2py -- web2py
item.description: Open redirect vulnerability in web2py versions prior to 2.22.5 allows a remote attacker to redirect a user to an arbitrary web site and conduct a phishing attack by having a user to access a specially crafted URL.
